headline: Equinix price target lowered to $1,033 from $1,114 at Scotiabank
summary: Scotiabank lowered the firm’s price target on Equinix (EQIX) to $1,033 from $1,114 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The company delivered “good” Q4 results as it continues to invest in expanding its retail and xScale capacity to respond to growing demand from customers, the analyst tells investors.
